n 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn87062169, 1930-01-31, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ak", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "seward (alaska)", "american newspapers", "seward", "united states", "alaska"], "subject_headings": ["American newspapers--Alaska", "Seward (Alaska)--Newspapers", "American newspapers", "Alaska", "Alaska--Seward", "United States--Alaska--Seward--Seward"], "subjects": [{"alaska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alaska&fo=json"}, {"american newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:american+newspapers&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"seward": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seward&fo=json"}, {"seward (alaska)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seward+%28alaska%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T22:53:56.797Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway (Seward, Alaska), January 31, 1930", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/1930-01-31/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn87062169", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/6690107f-53d5-549a-a446-0c78d4dfc567"], "batch": ["ak_icelandgull_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1923", "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Feb. 10, 1923-v. 29, no. 217 (Sept. 16, 1933). Sometimes published as: Seward gateway, Dec. 21, 1927-July 18, 1928; Aug. 5, 1929-Feb. 12, 1930. \"Independent.\" Numbering is irregular. Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Seward gateway (Seward, Alaska : 1933) 2993-7779 (DLC)sn 87062170 (OCoLC)15635455"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.512Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-08", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-08"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [60.1000798, -149.4421227], "location": ["united states", "seward", "alaska"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-149.4421227, 60.1000798], "number": ["3237", "2993-771x", "online resource", "2025-07-01t13:40:38.300000", "sn87062169", "8603701", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/1933-09-16/ed-1/", "1", "2024-05-12t17:51:13.897021", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/1923-02-10/ed-1/", "sn87062168", "sn87062170", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Seward gateway"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "catalog", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "seward daily gateway (seward, alaska) 1923-1933"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 48.04434, "shelf_id": "Newspaper F901 .S45", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "seward (alaska)", "american newspapers", "seward", "united states", "alaska"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:22:49.039Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn87062169/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2023270655/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1923", "dates": ["[1923 TO 1933]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began with volume VIII, number 34 (February 10, 1923); ceased with volume XXIX, number 217 (September 16, 1933). Sometimes published as: Seward gateway, Dec. 21, 1927-July 18, 1928; Aug. 5, 1929-Feb. 12, 1930. \"Independent.\" Numbering is irregular. Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Volume VIII, Number 34 (February 10, 1923); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 2, 2023). Volume XXIX, number 217 (September 16, 1933) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 2, 2023). Seward gateway (Seward, Alaska : 1933) 2993-7787 (DLC) 2023270656 (OCoLC)1392069938"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:10.725Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2023270655/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "seward", "alaska"], "number": ["online resource", "2023270656", "2020271966", "2023270655", "1392001920", "2993-7728", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Seward gateway"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "seward daily gateway (seward, alaska) 1923-1933 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 38.83706, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD F901 .S45", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "seward (alaska)", "american newspapers", "seward", "united states", "alaska"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:08:46.277Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2023270655/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271962/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1905", "dates": ["[1905 TO 1905]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began with vol. I, no. 1 (August 7, 1905); ceased with vol. I, no. 93 (November 22, 1905). Also available on microfilm from the Alaska Historical Society. Description based on: Vol. I, No. 1 (August 7, 1905); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 26, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Vol. I, No. 93 (November 22, 1905) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 26, 2020). Seward daily gateway (Seward, Alaska : 1905) 2692-6687 (DLC) 2020271963 (OCoLC)1159986219"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:52.256Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271962/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "seward", "alaska"], "number": ["2020271963", "online resource", "2021270897", "2020271962", "1159985970", "2692-6644", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "daily gateway (seward, alaska) 1905-1905 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 35.07359, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "seward (alaska)", "seward", "united states", "alaska"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:34.100Z", "title": "Daily gateway", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271962/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271963/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1905", "dates": ["[1905 TO 1914]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began with vol. I, no. 94 (November 23, 1905); ceased with vol. 8, number 241 (July 21, 1914). Also available on microfilm from the Alaska Historical Society. Description based on: Vol. I, No. 94 (November 23, 1905); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 26, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 8, No. 241 (July 21, 1914) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 26, 2020). Seward gateway (Seward, Alaska : 1914) 2692-6733 (DLC) 2020271964 (OCoLC)1160004269"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:52.256Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271963/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "seward", "alaska"], "number": ["2020271963", "1159986219", "2692-6687", "online resource", "2020271964", "2020271962", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "seward daily gateway (seward, alaska) 1905-1914 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 35.07359, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "seward (alaska)", "seward", "united states", "alaska"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:34.100Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271963/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271964/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1914", "dates": ["[1914 TO 1917]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began with vol. 8, no. 242 (July 22, 1914); ceased with vol. 10, no. 338 (Jan. 31, 1917). Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Merged with: Alaska evening post, to form: Seward gateway and the A